urinalysis_tests.action_step: Your urinalysis shows presence of nitrite. This is suggestive of bacterial urinary tract infection. A repeat test is recommended. Please consult our doctor for further medical advice.

urinalysis_tests.blood_test: Your Urine Bilirubin test is Negative
urinalysis_tests.action_step: Your urinalysis profile is within normal limits.

urinalysis_tests.blood_test: Your Urine Bilirubin test is Trace

urinalysis_tests.action_step: Your urinalysis shows high levels of bilirubin. This may indicate early sign of liver diseases. A repeat test is recommended. Please consult our doctor for further medical advice.

urinalysis_tests.blood_test: Your Urine Ketones test is Negative
urinalysis_tests.action_step: Your urinalysis profile is within normal limits.

urinalysis_tests.blood_test: Your Urine Ketones test is Trace

urinalysis_tests.action_step: Your urinalysis shows presence of ketones. This may due to a high protein diet, a low carbohydrate diet, or severe or strenuous exercise. It can also be an early indication of diabetes. Please consult our doctor for further medical advice.

urinalysis_tests.blood_test: Your Urine Protein test is Negative
urinalysis_tests.action_step: Your urine chemistry profile is within normal limits.

urinalysis_tests.blood_test: Your Urine Protein test is Trace
urinalysis_tests.action_step: Your urinalysis shows traces of protein. Occasionally, protein in the urine can be due to contamination at the time of urine collection. A repeat test is recommended. Please consult our doctor for further medical advice.

urinalysis_tests.blood_test: Your Urine Glucose test is Trace
